arf_enhance — standalone extraction of the arf-recog-adaptive-vad audio enhancer

This directory contains code derived from the arf-recog-adaptive-vad UniMRCP
plugin, specifically:

  src/arf_audio_enhance.c
  src/arf_audio_enhance.h

An STFT-based speech enhancer: Ephraim-Malah spectral-subtraction denoise,
adaptive high-pass de-boom, high-shelf de-muffle, a pumping-free leveler and a
soft-knee limiter. The DSP is unchanged; see arf_enhance.h for the list of
mechanical modifications made to remove the APR dependency.
